Shaping Chaos

Rank: 7
Uses: cantrip strand
      shape <object> <type> <detail>
Mana : varies (see "lore chaos2")

Bards have the ability to impose their will on raw chaos, temporarily
forcing it to match their view of reality, within certain limits.  
While some might consider these objects to be useless,
Bards know better.

For more information, see lore "chaos2"
